title: DC52 ZCORE [ZINC]
description:
A couple of people have asked before now, not to me directly about a similar series to cmc for DC. There has a number of people tried it but unlike CMC not kept it going. For a while i have been working to compile a DC comic pack, which covers all the comics released from New 52 series as listed in Wiki. I did try this before but was aborted due to time and a incomplete pack was uploaded hell if someone wants to carry it on they are welcome too i thought

Yet while the pack was incomplete it still got passed around a few places and it even returned back where i original started yet sadly with nothing add

So fast forward to now and i was having another look the DC52 went though only did a couple of folders cleaned them up and added new issues to them. With only them few folders its gone from original pack 27gig to 32gig with no end in sight and the time it took. So welcome to DC52 ZCORE or D5ZC for short, this be the main CORE pack you original download with CORE FILLERS or D5C F-X packs released in due course to fill in the gaps and tidy up mistakes

So once again this is a work in process MAIN CORE i hope to over the coming months add to the CORE it be simple impossble to keep adding to CORE and then upload it in one go..it be too ferking big and time consuming
